ßIN LOVING MEMORY OF BART MOORE-GILBERT, 1952-2015
Beloved father, lovely husband, dear friend, fabulous writer
We miss you so much, but you live on in our hearts
Love always, your 'sniggle' family, Anna, Maddy and Luke xxx"ņ
